PrecisApproval for the Halifax Port Corporation to make a By-law Amending the HALIFAX HARBOUR DUES BY-LAW in order to update some of the French terminology used therein as well as to improve the wording of the definition "harbour dues" in the English version.

precis:
Approval for the Halifax Port Corporation to make a By-law Amending the
HALIFAX HARBOUR DUES BY-LAW in order to update some of the French
terminology used therein as well as to improve the wording of the
definition "harbour dues" in the English version.
